<p style="margin: 0px;">Bank of America offers several insurance plans designed to provide income replacement in the event of serious injury or death.</p>
<H2 class="p" style="margin: 12px 0px 6px 0px; padding: 0px;"><span class="bd">Plan options</span></H2>
<ul>
	<li><span class="bd">Associate life insurance.</span> Provides financial support to your beneficiaries in the event of your death.</li>
	<li><span class="bd">Accidental death and dismemberment insurance.</span> Provides additional benefits if you or a covered dependent dies or suffers the loss of a limb, sight, hearing or paralysis as a result of an accident.</li>
	<li><span class="bd">Business travel accident insurance.</span> Increases benefits if injury or death occurs while traveling on company business.</li>
	<li><span class="bd">Dependent life insurance.</span> Assists with additional expenses incurred as a result of the death of a dependent.</li>
</ul>
